---
---

<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="section-inner">

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-copy">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">About</span>
        <h2 class="section-headline">Built for people who work across time zones.</h2>
        <p class="about-body">
          timetz was born out of frustration. Every existing tool required dropdown menus, manual UTC math, or a paid subscription just to answer a simple question: <em>"What time is 3pm in Mumbai for someone in London?"</em>
        </p>
        <p class="about-body">
          We built timetz to be the tool we always wanted — fast, natural, and free. Type the way you think, and get the answer in under a second.
        </p>

        <div class="why-box">
          <h3 class="why-title">Why timetz?</h3>
          <ul class="why-list">
            <li class="why-item">
              <span class="why-icon">⚡</span>
              <div>
                <strong>tz</strong> is the universal shorthand for timezone — used by engineers, Linux, and IANA worldwide. <strong>time + tz = timetz</strong>. Simple, memorable, obvious.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="why-item">
              <span class="why-icon">🌍</span>
              <div>
                It's short enough to type fast and clear enough to know exactly what it does. No fluff.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="why-item">
              <span class="why-icon">🔤</span>
              <div>
                <strong>timetz.com</strong> — four syllables, zero ambiguity. You'll never forget it.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">40+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Cities covered</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">&lt;1s</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Natural language parse</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">100%</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Free, no login</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">DST</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Daylight saving aware</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    background: var(--color-canvas);
    padding: 96px 24px;
  }

  .section-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Geist Mono Variable', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-mute);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .section-headline {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 40px;
    letter-spacing: -1.28px;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin: 0 0 24px;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 28px;
    color: var(--color-body);
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .about-body em {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .why-box {
    margin-top: 32px;
    background: var(--color-canvas-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .why-title {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.4px;
  }

  .why-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .why-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 22px;
    color: var(--color-body);
  }

  .why-icon {
    font-size: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .why-item strong { color: var(--color-ink); }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--color-canvas-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    line-height: 1;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-mute);
    line-height: 18px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .about-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-section { padding: 64px 20px; }
    .section-headline { font-size: 26px; }
    .about-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-section { padding: 48px 16px; }
    .section-headline { font-size: 22px; }
  }
</style>
